    <section id="rendering-expectations">
      <title>Rendering expectations</title>
      <p>The image addressed by the <xmlatt>keyref</xmlatt> or <xmlatt>href</xmlatt> attribute on
          <xmlelement>image</xmlelement> typically is rendered in the main flow of the content.</p>
      <div
        conref="../../common/conref-rendering-expectations.dita#conref-rendering-expectations/rendering-expectations-image-video"
      />
    </section>
